"^eker" <tag name="PERSON" value="start"/>Ahmed Pasha<tag name="PERSON" value="end"/> is one of the most important examples of the <tag name="MISC" value="start"/>Ottoman<tag name="MISC" value="end"/> military painters. He painted nature-related subjects such as forests, fruits, flowers, and animals with great skill.
